      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW SNEAKY (2) resumed in a Mix 6/7 at this track and ran into the frame when second over 425m (24.12). Sure to be fitter. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Rates highly and will give a great sight. MILA'S HAND (1) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (24.47) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Sale. Can find the frame this time. WAX OFF (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 24.12 beating LAKEVIEW SNEAKY. Comes through a solid form race last start. Bold showing expected again. BERNARDO SPLIT (7) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
